Package: SampleBuilder
Title: Functions for building sampling designs
Version: 2.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Paul",
           family = "Hegedus",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "paulhegedus@montana.edu",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6288-4345")),
    person(given = "Montana State University", 
           role = c("cph"))
    )
Description: For designing sampling designs such as transects, grids, and 
    random points. Transects are randomly built off of a user supplied line
    layer (roads, coastlines, etc.). Grids and points are based off of a 
    boundary layer or area of interest. 
